      "comment": "MUM'S TONKA (4) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at Warragul following on from a win (16.84) at this track the start prior. Form from his last run is proving strong. Ready to return to form. TRIVIA MASTER (6) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 20.18 beating Be A Secret. One of main contenders. EUROPA BLAZE (7) opened a winning account two back then missed the frame latest finishing a 5.5 lengths fourth last start at Geelong over 460m (26.31). Returns to the scene of his maiden win. Well placed here and should do much better. ASTON CRYPTO (2) will give backers a sight.",
